Rating: 3
Loved the marinade...it was delicious! The chicken thighs were a bit fatty. We'd probably make it again with chicken breasts. And the cucumber-dill sauce was delicious with it. I will definitely make it again.

Rating: 4
I love this recipe! I make "creamy dill dressing" to serve with this and skip the bacon - the marinade had enough flavor on its own. I also just use the marinade for plain grilled chicken. This is one of the best chicken marinades ever!

Rating: 2
I plan to serve this with Epicurious's Cucumber-Dill sauce (http://www.epicurious.com/run/recipe/view?id=5754), chopped lettuce and tomatoes, tabouleh and hummus (both store bought). Sounds great!

Rating: 3
In case of rain, you can easily do this under the broiler in the oven!

